metadata.name: Illogical Logic Four x Four
metadata.description: The Illogical Logic is a series on John Nash portrait that pays tribute to the Nash Equilibrium. By animating the payoff matrix into 3D cubes, each cube carry a value. Based on the values input, Nash's portrait appears in the cube which presents the dominant strategy. The two x two is constructed  with a 2 column by 2 row payoff matrix.
